    * fix(fog-of-war): render icons from exact sprite rect
    
    Stop sampling icons as synthetic NxN atlas cells. Pass selected sprite UV rect to shader and sample icon texture from that exact region, preserving RGBA alpha.
    
    * fix(fog-of-war): support per-icon sprite rect array
    
    Pass UV rect array for FogIconSprites and sample rect by sequential icon-grid index. This supports different rect for each sprite while preserving RGBA icon blending.
    
    * fix(fog-of-war): fallback icon rect when array data is unavailable
    
    If per-icon UV rect array returns zero-sized data on backend, shader falls back to primary icon rect to prevent dark squares and keep icons visible.
    
    * feat(fog-of-war): make icon sequence symmetric across grid
    
    Use mirrored icon-grid coordinates to preserve sequential ordering while enforcing X/Y symmetry for icon distribution.
    
